{"tid":256201,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"播唔到星期日足總盃決賽 賠多三個月作為補償","createTime":"2017-05-24T10:57:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-24T15:21:43.000Z","uid":11885,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9a56f3f5638519f075185c0f850b20c016c1f47d","tid":256201,"uid":11885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T10:57:08.000Z","msg":"再次傳出財困的樂視，一直未有影響到香港業務，但樂視體育今日公佈，因節目調整，本週日(5月28日)凌晨在LeSports HK平台直播的英格蘭足總盃(FA Cup)決賽(阿仙奴對車路士)，將無法播出。LeSports HK對本次受影響的用戶鄭重致歉，將提供3個月超級體育組合作為補償。<br />\n<br />\n本報向樂視香港公關查詢無法播放的原因，只獲回覆「因節目調整」，賠償方面亦只得3個月超級體育組合。樂視只表示，如有查詢，可聯繫客戶服務熱線：3956 6666<br />\n<br />\n據了解，與樂視合作播放英超的nowTV並沒有直播的英格蘭足總盃(FA Cup)，如今樂視無法播出，屆時香港可能將沒有合法途徑收看足總盃決賽。<br />\n<br />\n本月初，樂視體育已出現播放問題，包括「韋斯咸：熱刺」英超賽事和一場NBA賽事，令用戶怨聲載道。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170524&amp;s=7015342&amp;a=56737069 \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170524%26s%3D7015342%26a%3D56737069%20&d=K6hFM7A%2BqeP3hI5k7AlIvARJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=878abba5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170524%26s%3D7015342%26a%3D56737069%20&h=31dec82a\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170524&amp;s=7015342&amp;a=56737069 </a><br />\n<br />\n樂視你無撚野呀？"},{"pid":"bb2c24048cdae50695b42b9b9487e2b090776942","tid":256201,"uid":11885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T10:57:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a40ff453715981a5ebea218bb3030fb98e15bcda","tid":256201,"uid":4444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T10:58:00.000Z","msg":"決賽先播唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de7df3db2ef3b513b5b516c30a93662fc43efbfc","tid":256201,"uid":11885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl